WEBVTT

00:00:19.162 --> 00:00:24.349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:25.661
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.662 --> 00:00:27.741
♪You're always♪

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:32.391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.392 --> 00:00:35.124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:36.691
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:42.481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.895
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 14=

00:01:00.019 --> 00:01:01.379
No matter where I am,

00:01:02.180 --> 00:01:03.740
can you always find me?

00:01:04.779 --> 00:01:05.700
I'll find you

00:01:05.859 --> 00:01:06.700
and protect you.

00:01:23.419 --> 00:01:24.379
Mu Zhiyu,

00:01:25.109 --> 00:01:26.338
my phone has been ringing nonstop

00:01:26.339 --> 00:01:28.379
with calls from the board
early this morning.

00:01:28.660 --> 00:01:30.338
Do you know what you did last night?

00:01:30.339 --> 00:01:31.899
Stop beating around the bush.

00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:33.240
I'm not in the mood for nonsense.

00:01:33.240 --> 00:01:34.680
Last night, you and Shen Jibai

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:36.700
were photographed
drunk and behaving improperly.

00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:38.819
This has greatly affected Mu Group.

00:01:39.660 --> 00:01:40.418
The board

00:01:40.419 --> 00:01:41.860
wants an explanation from you.

00:01:41.979 --> 00:01:43.379
That's my private matter.

00:01:43.679 --> 00:01:45.379
There's no need for me
to explain it for you.

00:01:45.460 --> 00:01:47.338
You're now the heiress of Mu Group.

00:01:47.339 --> 00:01:49.058
Your every move
represents the company.

00:01:49.059 --> 00:01:50.140
Do you understand?

00:01:50.859 --> 00:01:51.739
Are you done?

00:01:52.979 --> 00:01:54.179
If you're done, please leave.

00:01:55.100 --> 00:01:56.379
Since you don't appreciate it,

00:01:56.979 --> 00:01:58.780
you can explain it
to the board yourself.

00:02:10.750 --> 00:02:12.207
(WeChat)

00:02:17.675 --> 00:02:18.882
(WeChat)

00:02:24.539 --> 00:02:25.259
(Boss,)

00:02:25.379 --> 00:02:27.099
(are you really together with Mu Zhiyu?)

00:02:27.300 --> 00:02:28.618
(When did that happen?)

00:02:28.619 --> 00:02:30.259
(How come I knew nothing about it?)

00:02:30.740 --> 00:02:32.379
(What nonsense are you talking about?)

00:02:34.875 --> 00:02:37.932
(Yan Muqing)

00:02:46.980 --> 00:02:48.659
Nothing happened between us last night.

00:02:48.860 --> 00:02:50.379
Someone framed us.

00:02:51.659 --> 00:02:52.658
Go investigate

00:02:52.659 --> 00:02:54.379
who took those photos.

00:03:09.539 --> 00:03:11.019
They're together all the time.

00:03:11.020 --> 00:03:12.539
It's normal if they're dating.

00:03:12.779 --> 00:03:14.218
Who would've thought Ms. Mu

00:03:14.219 --> 00:03:16.259
would fall for a bodyguard?

00:03:36.659 --> 00:03:37.818
I'll find out

00:03:37.819 --> 00:03:39.259
who took your photo last night.

00:03:39.260 --> 00:03:41.099
Who took the photos isn't important.

00:03:41.300 --> 00:03:43.338
We both know

00:03:43.339 --> 00:03:44.419
who the mastermind behind is.

00:03:44.420 --> 00:03:46.060
Xu Mingzhu came to see me last night.

00:03:46.379 --> 00:03:48.060
She already knows what's in the will.

00:03:48.099 --> 00:03:49.539
The reason she did all this

00:03:49.740 --> 00:03:51.379
is to force us into getting married.

00:03:52.339 --> 00:03:55.060
Xu Mingzhu is so eager for me to marry.

00:03:55.980 --> 00:03:57.818
What is she planning?

00:03:57.819 --> 00:03:58.740
The inheritance.

00:03:59.619 --> 00:04:00.900
Why did Xu Mingzhu

00:04:01.300 --> 00:04:03.539
ask you to keep an eye on me?

00:04:03.659 --> 00:04:06.139
She wants the password
to a bank safety deposit box.

00:04:06.140 --> 00:04:08.019
(If I want to deal with Xu Mingzhu,)

00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:09.620
(I must obtain the inheritance.)

00:04:09.939 --> 00:04:11.259
(But according to the will,)

00:04:11.379 --> 00:04:12.900
(I have to get married first.)

00:04:13.700 --> 00:04:15.659
(And I don't even have
someone to marry.)

00:04:18.820 --> 00:04:20.940
(Maybe he could be a suitable choice.)

00:04:22.460 --> 00:04:23.499
What about you?

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:26.020
Do you want to marry me?

00:04:27.260 --> 00:04:30.260
Marriage isn't child's play.
You must consider it carefully.

00:04:30.940 --> 00:04:32.700
It's too early for us to discuss this.

00:04:33.859 --> 00:04:34.979
What I mean

00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:36.379
is a fake marriage.

00:04:36.380 --> 00:04:37.379
No!

00:04:37.380 --> 00:04:38.220
I won't allow that!

00:04:39.419 --> 00:04:40.340
Yu,

00:04:40.539 --> 00:04:41.699
if you want a fake husband,

00:04:41.700 --> 00:04:42.859
why not choose me?

00:04:43.099 --> 00:04:45.099
We know each other well.

00:04:45.500 --> 00:04:46.418
His approach to you

00:04:46.419 --> 00:04:47.619
is suspicious.

00:04:47.900 --> 00:04:49.338
Don't be fooled by him.

00:04:49.339 --> 00:04:50.220
Mr. He,

00:04:51.060 --> 00:04:52.900
watch your words.

00:04:53.179 --> 00:04:54.019
Without evidence,

00:04:54.020 --> 00:04:55.260
don't make baseless accusations.

00:04:56.820 --> 00:04:58.820
I'll definitely catch you
with something someday.

00:05:09.859 --> 00:05:10.979
Let's begin.

00:05:13.979 --> 00:05:16.899
A lot has been going on
at the company recently.

00:05:16.900 --> 00:05:18.979
The chairman passed away suddenly.

00:05:19.219 --> 00:05:20.738
As the acting president,

00:05:20.739 --> 00:05:23.619
I should return the company shares
and management rights

00:05:23.739 --> 00:05:27.020
to the chairman's only daughter, Zhiyu.

00:05:28.060 --> 00:05:29.379
However, before his death,

00:05:29.380 --> 00:05:31.020
the chairman still had
an unfinished wish.

00:05:31.060 --> 00:05:32.739
It was written into his will.

00:05:32.979 --> 00:05:33.900
Zhiyu

00:05:34.219 --> 00:05:36.739
must fulfill the chairman's wish

00:05:37.099 --> 00:05:39.020
before inheriting everything.

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:46.460
My dad did make some requests
in his will.

00:05:47.539 --> 00:05:49.739
But that doesn't stop me
from taking over the company.

00:05:51.060 --> 00:05:52.499
The chairman's greatest wish

00:05:52.500 --> 00:05:54.580
was for you to marry
and have a child soon.

00:05:54.859 --> 00:05:56.140
Before that happens,

00:05:56.179 --> 00:05:59.259
I can help share some of the company's
responsibilities.

00:05:59.260 --> 00:06:01.099
Ms. Xu, what you mean is

00:06:01.419 --> 00:06:03.460
that until I fulfill my dad's wish,

00:06:04.580 --> 00:06:06.539
Mu Group will still be run by you?

00:06:07.940 --> 00:06:10.260
I certainly hope you can take over soon.

00:06:10.979 --> 00:06:12.819
But the chairman's last wish

00:06:12.820 --> 00:06:14.340
must be respected.

00:06:14.779 --> 00:06:16.659
Marriage is a major life decision.

00:06:16.900 --> 00:06:18.859
I can't make such a choice lightly.

00:06:20.140 --> 00:06:21.619
Isn't Zhiyu

00:06:21.659 --> 00:06:24.812
already dating someone recently?

00:06:24.812 --> 00:06:26.338
- Right.
- That might not be appropriate.

00:06:26.339 --> 00:06:27.680
I don't think that's a good idea.

00:06:28.219 --> 00:06:29.539
What about the company's image?

00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:32.179
There are no plans to get married
at the moment.

00:06:32.739 --> 00:06:34.940
Then I'll wait until your relationship
becomes stable.

00:06:35.179 --> 00:06:36.738
As long as you two get engaged,

00:06:36.739 --> 00:06:38.700
I'll step down

00:06:39.419 --> 00:06:41.499
and hand over the company to you

00:06:41.500 --> 00:06:42.739
with peace of mind.

00:06:43.020 --> 00:06:44.780
Ms. Xu,

00:06:46.219 --> 00:06:47.538
you've thought everything through.

00:06:47.539 --> 00:06:49.299
(Once you two get married,)

00:06:49.339 --> 00:06:51.380
(I can quickly seize the inheritance.)

00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:54.380
Zhiyu,

00:06:54.820 --> 00:06:56.699
is the person you're dating

00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:59.580
the bodyguard who appeared
in the news today?

00:06:59.739 --> 00:07:01.659
This is personal.

00:07:01.779 --> 00:07:03.418
I don't think
I need to report it to you.

00:07:03.419 --> 00:07:04.579
But you represent

00:07:04.580 --> 00:07:06.098
the company's image now.

00:07:06.099 --> 00:07:08.179
You can't choose
your partner carelessly.

00:07:08.940 --> 00:07:11.340
Not to mention that a bodyguard's status
is far below yours.

00:07:11.539 --> 00:07:12.699
As a bodyguard,

00:07:12.700 --> 00:07:14.220
being involved with his employer

00:07:14.260 --> 00:07:15.778
violates professional ethics.

00:07:15.779 --> 00:07:16.338
Yes.

00:07:16.339 --> 00:07:17.059
Right.

00:07:17.140 --> 00:07:19.340
How can she date a bodyguard?

00:07:21.060 --> 00:07:23.340
As long as Zhiyu likes him,

00:07:23.460 --> 00:07:25.299
I support it.

00:07:25.940 --> 00:07:29.340
Besides, Captain Shen has saved her
more than once.

00:07:29.539 --> 00:07:30.939
Their relationship

00:07:30.940 --> 00:07:32.900
isn't for outsiders to judge.

00:07:33.620 --> 00:07:34.940
(Xu Mingzhu,)

00:07:35.460 --> 00:07:37.900
(you're really doing everything you can
to shove us together.)

00:07:46.620 --> 00:07:47.499
Yu,

00:07:48.739 --> 00:07:49.820
I've been waiting for you.

00:07:50.659 --> 00:07:51.780
What's the matter?

00:07:51.940 --> 00:07:53.220
Where's Shen Jibai?

00:07:53.299 --> 00:07:54.900
I was about to talk to you about him.

00:07:55.020 --> 00:07:57.280
I found out that he fought
in illegal boxing matches overseas.

00:07:57.339 --> 00:07:57.939
Look.

00:07:57.940 --> 00:07:58.900
This is the evidence.

00:08:02.900 --> 00:08:04.019
I already knew

00:08:04.020 --> 00:08:05.418
about that.

00:08:05.419 --> 00:08:06.499
Yu,

00:08:06.580 --> 00:08:08.098
you should stay away from him.

00:08:08.099 --> 00:08:09.179
Are you finished?

00:08:10.260 --> 00:08:11.940
If you're done, please leave.

00:08:15.700 --> 00:08:16.739
Yu,

00:08:17.500 --> 00:08:19.579
I know you're in
a difficult situation now.

00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:20.738
You have to marry someone

00:08:20.739 --> 00:08:22.178
to obtain the inheritance.

00:08:22.179 --> 00:08:23.338
But once two people marry,

00:08:23.339 --> 00:08:25.418
many things become complicated.

00:08:25.419 --> 00:08:27.419
Shen Jibai is not trustworthy.

00:08:27.700 --> 00:08:29.380
Don't let him deceive you.

00:08:31.980 --> 00:08:33.099
He Min,

00:08:33.500 --> 00:08:35.259
I know you mean well.

00:08:35.459 --> 00:08:36.580
But I have

00:08:36.819 --> 00:08:38.099
my own judgment.

00:08:40.500 --> 00:08:41.420
Yu,

00:08:42.819 --> 00:08:44.099
I would do anything

00:08:44.539 --> 00:08:45.420
for you.

00:08:46.539 --> 00:08:48.060
Can you give me a chance?

00:08:48.100 --> 00:08:49.420
I don't want to hold you back.

00:08:51.980 --> 00:08:54.300
You shouldn't waste your time on me.

00:08:55.020 --> 00:08:56.818
Then why him, but not me?

00:08:56.819 --> 00:08:59.019
Because I see you as my best friend.

00:09:03.020 --> 00:09:04.979
I don't want anything to change
between us.

00:09:09.020 --> 00:09:10.060
Friends?

00:09:12.419 --> 00:09:13.779
Can we only ever be friends?

00:09:31.179 --> 00:09:33.240
Boss, the test report is out.

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:35.240
I've already asked a courier
to deliver it to you.

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:36.280
It should arrive very soon.

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:36.820
Alright.

00:09:41.459 --> 00:09:42.019
Hello?

00:09:42.020 --> 00:09:43.019
Are you Shen Jibai?

00:09:43.020 --> 00:09:43.499
Yes.

00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:44.139
Your parcel.

00:09:44.140 --> 00:09:44.739
Thank you.

00:09:53.300 --> 00:09:54.074
(Test Result)

00:09:54.075 --> 00:09:59.370
(Conclusion: Mu Chenzhou is confirmed
to be Shen Jibai's biological father)

00:10:00.125 --> 00:10:02.536
(Mu Chenzhou is
my biological father?)

00:10:02.537 --> 00:10:03.482
(Mu Chenzhou is confirmed
to be Shen Jibai's biological father)

00:10:05.059 --> 00:10:09.139
(The man who just died
for unknown reason was my real father.)

00:10:09.299 --> 00:10:10.820
(Then Mu Zhiyu...)

00:10:10.980 --> 00:10:12.259
(We're siblings.)

00:10:22.299 --> 00:10:23.139
(No.)

00:10:23.179 --> 00:10:24.058
(Impossible.)

00:10:24.059 --> 00:10:25.180
(I don't believe it.)

00:10:25.419 --> 00:10:26.859
(I need to keep digging.)

00:10:27.059 --> 00:10:29.080
(I have to find out the truth
about our relationship.)

00:10:40.737 --> 00:10:44.967
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:10:45.107 --> 00:10:49.476
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:10:49.477 --> 00:10:53.967
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:10:58.187 --> 00:11:02.126
♪Shadows move around♪

00:11:02.127 --> 00:11:06.736
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:11:06.737 --> 00:11:11.267
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:11:14.867 --> 00:11:20.657
♪Don't slip away♪

00:11:23.107 --> 00:11:27.676
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:27.677 --> 00:11:32.076
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:32.077 --> 00:11:36.397
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:36.417 --> 00:11:40.397
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:40.867 --> 00:11:45.176
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:45.177 --> 00:11:49.506
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:49.507 --> 00:11:53.816
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:53.817 --> 00:11:59.967
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪